Welcome to Gitsby.

Or, put simply, a collection of pieces of code to perform usual tasks that one might want to do while doing Science at the Gatsby Computational Neuroscience Unit.

Checkout the repository or download whatever file is of interest to you.

Please do not break anything.

===============================

CONTENTS:

- General Python tools
    - Plotting
    - Data handling
- General Matlab
- PBS interfaces
    - General shell scripts
    - Matlab script 'farmout'
    - Python package

================================
